        <abstract> 
<p>Regularly attends Owen’s lectures. Owen at pains to show groups are not linked. Thus makes <hi rend="italic">Lepidosiren</hi> appear fish-like.</p> 
            <p>GRW thinks embryology will become chief guide to insect classification. But contradictions between classification based on embryological and adult characters do occur.</p>
        </abstract>
